<text top="595" left="45" width="3" height="9" font="5">(</text>
<text top="595" left="49" width="3" height="9" font="7">r</text>
<text top="595" left="55" width="47" height="9" font="5">= 0.82–0.85,</text>
<text top="595" left="104" width="5" height="9" font="7">p</text>
<text top="593" left="111" width="7" height="12" font="9">&lt;</text>
<text top="595" left="121" width="169" height="9" font="5">0.001). A moderate negative correlation was</text>
<text top="607" left="45" width="245" height="9" font="5">observed between the KPI and the cognitive-congruency metric</text>
<text top="618" left="45" width="245" height="9" font="5">calculated on the beta range (16–18 Hz). However, it failed to</text>
<text top="630" left="45" width="77" height="9" font="5">reach significance (</text>
<text top="630" left="122" width="3" height="9" font="7">r</text>
<text top="630" left="130" width="5" height="9" font="5">=</text>
<text top="630" left="140" width="7" height="7" font="8">−</text>
